column5: Nice to see you didnt give up.
Good stuff. Nothing wrong with your other hat!

hat is fine ...the look on the young lads face is the reason ALL of us invest into this sport we call fishing ( nicely done young man yours is bigger then the other one  ) I think i recognize the photo on your shirt though...is that from Americas Most Wanted? Just kidding around guys....nice shootin to the two of you ...
Take a closer look at that first fish and appreciate it for the detail and colour of the scales and such. Just a carp but nice looking fish man!
Awesome !!!! Glad you stuck around.Your little guy has all the right moves Nice carp Bud !!!  Paul
Nice catch.....good to see another report from you dude
That first fish is a sucker isn't it? And a big one too - nice going!
damn those are some big suckers!!  Defiantly a size up from the ones we get down here
Yep, thats a very nice sucker!!!!
